<div class="row">
    <div class="four_part">
        <h2>Human-Generated Waste and Its Impact on Climate Change</h2>
        <p>
            Human civilization has experienced rapid industrialization, urbanization,
            and population growth in the past two centuries. As a consequence, the generation of waste,
            in its various forms, has surged dramatically. From the mountains of plastic in our oceans to the noxious fumes from our factories and cars,
            human-generated waste has become a pressing environmental concern.
            Let’s delves into the intricate relationship between human waste and climate change,
            highlighting the imperative need to address this multifaceted challenge.
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="six_part">
        <img src="~/lib/bootstrap/dist/css/pexels-josh-sorenson-1054391.jpg" alt="Description of image 1" class="six-part-image">
